  "keyFeatures": [
    "Policy-based design for flexible syscall strategies",
    "Automatic syscall number resolution from ntdll.dll",
    "Multiple allocation methods (section with SEC_NO_CHANGE, heap, virtual memory)",
    "Three stub generation approaches (direct, gadget, exception-based)",
    "Hook detection and evasion via neighboring syscall resolution",
    "Compile-time string hashing for operational security",
    "Header-only C++20 library with zero runtime dependencies",
    "Support for both x86 and x64 Windows platforms"
  ],
